                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1205473997" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1205473997" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1205473997">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63928497/">暄泫</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">对于我来说是一个挺新的角度，之前从来没有想过资产的所有权对于资本运作方面有那么大影响。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1195120238">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1195120238" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1195120238" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1195120238">有用</a>
